column4: さて、お店を手伝わなきゃ。
column5: Now then, I have to get back to helping out at the store.
column11: Now then, I have to get back to helping out at the store.

column4:
今度こそ、お客さんも
いっぱい来ると思うし。

たまたまザ・バーガーが
壊れただけなんだけど。
column5: With the Automen on a rampage, it juuust so happened that {The Burger} got accidentally destroyed.
